data.description: Come see this beautiful custom-built home in Frisco Ridge!  This charming home features four bedrooms and two full bathrooms downstairs with a large bonus room (optional 5th bedroom) and half bath upstairs (plumbed for future shower).  The interior finishes are beautiful and timeless! This thoughtful floor plan flows beautifully into the different areas of the home and is sprinkled with custom features throughout. Enjoy the views of the trees and greenbelt through the many well-placed windows. There are no backyard neighbors and room for a pool! Neighborhood amenities include a soccer field, basketball court, playground, pond, and walking trails.  This home is in Banner Schools which is K-8 and you get to choose your high school!  This home has all the extras like irrigation, storm shelter, over-sized 3rd garage with utility sink and more! Do not miss this beautiful home! The seller just spoke to their mortgage company who said that the 3.25% current VA loan rate is assumable (terms and conditions apply)!
